Module Description:

Integrate Imagemagick into Drupal.

Files: imagemagick2.inc, README

Copy the imagemagick2.inc into the includes diretory to get the advanced imagemagick2 toolkit option in the administer->settings->Image Handling Toolit.

Select the Advanced Imagemagick Toolkit.

The default image.module resize should work fine with this. Additional functionality will be written as a new module called image2.module

Present Image Manipulation Functions:
	1) Resize 
	2) Crop
	3) Blur
	4) Rotate
	5) Blur
	6) Charcoal
	7) Emboss
	8) Sharpen
	9) Swirl
	10) Spread
	11) Solarize
	12) Flip
	13) Flop
	14) Magnify
	15) Minify
	16) Normalize
	17) Trim
	18) Transparent


